                    <li>Chocolatey unifies your approaches to software installation and tracking on Windows.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 text-center">

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="py-3 py-lg-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 text-center">

            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h2 class="mb-3 text-center"><strong>Organizations like yours turn to Chocolatey for Business when:</strong></h2>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>You have a need for a supported approach.</li>
                    <li>You need to move quickly to install/upgrade software. Chocolatey's Package Builder and a good configuration manager can achieve software upgrades across your entire organization in 10 minutes or less from determination to implementation.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Why is this better? The faster you can move to update 3rd party software (and internal software) reduces security risks for your organization.</p>
                <p>
                    Chocolatey for Business is the enterprise offering that enables companies to adopt a DevOps approach to managing their Windows environment, allowing you to deliver applications to your users more reliably and faster.
                    Chocolatey Open Source is great for individuals to get started on automating their Windows management, but when you have complex, critical infrastructure managed by teams, Chocolatey for Business offers more. 
                    With our business editions you get all of the benefits of open source Chocolatey together with enhanced capabilities, integrations, and the peace of mind of having a supported platform.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="py-3 py-lg-5 bg-white">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h2 class="mb-3 text-center"><strong>Deliver End to End automation through customised packages</strong></h2>
                <p>
                    Save time and reduce complexity by creating packages directly from software installers in seconds.
                    We often hear from our customers that they are increasingly under pressure to deliver more software applications faster and reliably. With multiple versions to support it has only become time consuming and complex. Chocolatey for Business helps by automating the the task of application installation. Chocolatey can figure out how to install the various components and creates an entire package surrounding the process.  Effort can be reduced from hours to minutes. Whilst also reducing human error and ensuring consistency. By leveraging our powerful platform you can begin to build your customised packages for various use cases. Allowing you to automate the entire lifecycle in minutes.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 text-center">

            </div>
